==English==
=== Etymology ===
From Latin ''[[carpere]]'', to [[pluck]].

=== Noun ===
'''carpet''' ([[uncountable]] and [[countable]]; plural: [[carpets]])

# a fabric used as a floor covering
# a surface resembling a carpet
# a [[rug]]

====Derived terms====
*[[carpet bombing]]
*[[flying carpet]]
*[[on the carpet]]

